mutation ($payload:AdminCreateLangInput!)
{
	adminCreateLang (payload:$payload)

		id
		name
		image
		iso6392
		iso6393
		ietf
		sort
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

graphql.query:
query ($query:[QueryStatementInput])
{
	adminGetLangs (query: $query)
	{
		id
		name
		image
		iso6392
		iso6393
		ietf
		sort
		isActive
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}

		iso6392

query ($id:ID)

}
